WEBVTT

00:10:59.637 --> 00:11:03.174
She wanted to rest in peace
next to her son,

00:11:03.198 --> 00:11:07.874
who had died many years before
she emigrated to Argentina.

00:11:08.759 --> 00:11:14.455
My grandmother lived a life
full of deep connections

00:11:14.479 --> 00:11:16.431
and indestructible ties,

00:11:16.455 --> 00:11:21.129
including those separated by
distances or oceans

00:11:21.153 --> 00:11:22.603
or even death.

00:11:23.071 --> 00:11:27.248
She had many identities:
matriarch, farmer,

00:11:27.272 --> 00:11:32.332
businesswoman, Korean, immigrant,
mother, grandmother.